## E0 Gate Decision

Sequential_P@1 (0.249) - Flat_P@1 (0.302) = -5.3%p → FAIL (requires +5%p)
Parallel_P@1 (0.296) - Flat_P@1 (0.302) = -0.6%p → FAIL (requires +5%p)

2-Layer does NOT improve over 1-Layer on this GT set.
Sequential's server-level hard gate hurts recall significantly (0.352 vs 0.527).
Parallel recovers via RRF fusion but doesn't beat Flat.

Proceed to E1 for deeper strategy analysis.
